{
  "chapter": 47,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十七回 计中之计。花无缺给铁心兰喂下解药后，追问谁下的毒。江别鹤联合一名伪装轿夫的高手，巧妙地将下毒和劫镖的罪名栽赃给铁无双。轿夫口齿伶俐，以层层推理将铁无双逼入绝境。铁无双盛怒出手却被轿夫击败，受了内伤。花无缺给了铁无双和赵香灵半天时间了断，子时再来。铁无双万念俱灰，欲自尽了断。罗九献计先下手为强，绑架段合肥父女以要挟江别鹤。赵香灵犹豫再三后同意。罗九、罗三带人闯入段合肥宅院，以暗器和高强武功轻松制服守卫，成功绑架段合肥父女。小鱼儿暗中跟随，识破轿夫身份，并发现江别鹤与罗氏兄弟早有勾结，故意放任绑架发生，使铁无双更加百口莫辩。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁下的毒？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下的确不知。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这必定是有人栽赃！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这药难道真不是铁老英雄与赵庄主买来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟什么都不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你们明明知道，昨夜你们也亲眼瞧见的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟只瞧见药自己来了，却不知是谁送来的，说不定是张三，说不定是李四，也说不定是……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也说不定就是铁老英雄的门下，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "阁下还有何活说？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "你两人怎敢如此？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟只是说老实话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤昆仲当真是信义之人，在下好生相敬，但铁老英雄么……嘿嘿。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁姑娘！铁姑娘醒来了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯……我冷得很！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "铁姑娘可知是被谁下毒的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我是中毒了么？我也不知道是谁下毒的……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只知吃了铁无双送来的两粒枣子，就全身发冷，直打冷战，不到片刻，已晕迷不省人事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你……你为何要血口喷人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "阁下此刻还想狡赖，未免不是大丈夫了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁！老夫与她一不相识，二无仇恨，为何要害她？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花公子，你听这话如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我等出手之前，总得要人口服心服。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正该如此。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江大侠有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "铁老前辈方才说的话，你听到了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "小人听得清清楚楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "你说他是否有加害铁姑娘的道理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "那么，这毒不是铁老英雄下的了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "是铁老英雄下的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "你为何又说是铁老英雄下的毒呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因他虽无相害铁姑娘之意，却有毒杀花公子之心。他下毒本是要害花公子的，只不过铁姑娘首当其冲而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁老英雄与花公子也素无冤仇，又为何要害花公子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此，老夫为何要害人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要杀人自然有几个原因，一是嫉妒，二是仇恨，还有自己若是做了见不得人的事怕被人发觉……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "老夫一生顶天立地，你这奴才竟敢道老夫做了见不得人的事！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "小人可不敢说这话，这话可是铁老英雄你自己说的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，好好，当着许多朋友，老夫倒要听听你这奴才说老夫究竟做了些什么见不得人的事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见不得人的事也有许多种，譬如说偷鸡摸狗，这种算是小的，劫人镖银，杀人性命，这就算是大的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "你……你说老夫劫了谁的镖银？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "譬如说段合肥老爷的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段合肥？你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "城里人人都知道，段老爷和赵庄主是对头，段老爷子买货的银子若被劫，货物进不来，这城里岂非就没有人和赵庄主抢生意了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵然如此，这和老夫又有何关系？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁老英雄若是在暗中劫了段合肥的镖，不但赵庄主要重重酬谢，而且那一笔镖银铁老英雄正也可消受了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "好，好，你……你再说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁老英雄本以为这件事做的神不知，鬼不觉，江湖中纵然有人调查此事，也算计不到铁老英雄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_jiao_fu",
      "text": "好可恶的奴才，老夫先打烂你这张利嘴！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "铁老前辈毕竟已老了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "前辈还有什么话说，在下等俱都洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下还有话说，试问那毒真是铁老英雄下的，他送礼时怎会用自己的名字？又怎会将解药放在这里，难道等着阁下来抓人抓赃么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "轿夫",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "若是凡俗之辈，自然不会这样做的，但铁老英雄纵横江湖数十年，是何等见识，他这样做法，正是叫别人不信此事真是他做的，这岂非说比那种此地无银三百两的做法高明十倍、百倍。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "事已至此，公子意下如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事若被天下英雄知晓，天下英雄俱都难容。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "此刻方值正午，我再给两位半天时间，两位可自思该如何了断，今夜子时，我当再来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "在下素仰老前辈侠名，本待好生结纳。谁知……唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "气死老夫……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "前辈赶紧到后面歇歇，先将养伤势……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今夜子时便是你我大限，养好伤势又有何用？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……只怕也未必，他们人已走了……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们人虽走了，老夫难道还能逃走不成……咳咳，不想老夫一世清名，到老来竟要死于屈辱！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事到如今，老夫已无处可去，无路可走，与其等到子时，倒当真不如自己先作个了断也罢！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "前辈切切不可如此，事情只怕还有转机……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至今，我等已是百口莫辩，除非寻得出那真凶……但人海茫茫何处去寻那真凶？更何况只有半天的工夫。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "半天……子时……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤呀江别鹤，花无缺呀花无缺！老夫并不怪你，事到如此……咳咳，你们也只有如此做了，你们能多给老夫半天时间，已是大仁大义，老夫……咳……老夫还该感激于你……咳咳。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "贤昆仲难道也无以救我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "铁老英雄忧郁太过，依在下看来，此事倒也简单。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "快请指教。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "事到如今，你我只有先下手为强，将段合肥与他女儿擒来，好叫江别鹤投鼠忌器，不敢下手。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "此事万万做不得，若是如此做了，天下武林中人，岂非真要以为劫镖、下毒之事俱是我等所为？我等岂非更是百口莫辩。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "庄主怎地如此执著，需知如此行事，只不过是暂时从权之计，一面稳住江别鹤等人，一面去寻访真凶，等真凶寻到，真相大白后，再好生将段家父女送还，那时江湖中有谁敢说庄主不是的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……在下还是觉得此事……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "庄主若不肯行此妙计，以那江别鹤与花无缺的武功，庄主要想逃过今夜子时之限只怕是难如登天的了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来也只有如此了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是，那段合肥仆役如云，要想自他庄院中将他父女劫来，也绝非易事，这得有千军万马中取上将首级的本事。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个倒不用庄主担忧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻花无缺与江别鹤恐必不会防备有此一着，更不会去防护段氏父女，除了这两人外，别的人都可不虑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道两位肯仗义援手？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "食君之禄，怎能不忠君之事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "贤昆仲如此高义，在下真不知该如何报答才是。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "庄主切莫如此多礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事不宜迟，在下此刻就要去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "贤昆仲若有所需，但请吩咐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "别的不用，只请庄主派八位家丁，抬两顶小轿跟随着我兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个容易……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两个轿子此刻让我兄弟坐坐，等会儿就要轮到段合肥父女坐了，他父女只怕也不比我兄弟轻。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "段合肥的庄院，你们可认得么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhuang_jia_ding",
      "speaker_name": "赵庄家丁",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "自然认得，咱们好几次想去放火烧他房子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，咱们这就走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhuang_jia_ding",
      "speaker_name": "赵庄家丁",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "前面就是段合肥的猪窝了，罗爷瞧该怎么办？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笔直抬进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhuang_jia_ding",
      "speaker_name": "赵庄家丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段合肥的守门狗不少，若被他们咬一口，岂非冤枉。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们只管往里面抬就是，那些守门狗决计咬不着你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_zhai_zhuang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "段宅庄丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，你们是干什么的？站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们是来抬猪的，让开！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_zhai_zhuang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "段宅庄丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "狗养的，你们是来找死么……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "守门狗不叫了，你们还不走。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_zhai_zhuang_ding",
      "speaker_name": "段宅庄丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人呀，来人呀，门外有恶鬼闯来了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伙计们，往前走呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "轿子里暗青子扎手，伙计们先退。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "射人先射马，先将抬轿子的做了再说。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位难道不认得区区在下了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位既不认得在下，在下也只有不认得各位了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想这里竞还有杨家枪的门人，这一招凤点头看来至少也有十五年的火候，算得上是好枪法。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_da_han",
      "text": "彭念祖彭老师可好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "你认得他老人家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不认得！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三位如今可认得区区在下了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如今各位总该认得在下了吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fu_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段府武师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "认得……认得……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位认得我是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fu_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段府武师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你老人家是……是……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我姓罗，叫罗九。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fu_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段府武师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错不错，你老人家是罗九爷。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位既然认得在下，那真是再好也没有了，就烦两位带我去拜见拜见段合肥段老爷子如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fu_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段府武师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这区区小事，两位都不肯答应么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fu_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "段府武师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，就请……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
